  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research settings to predict hemolysis in centrifugal blood pumps under ventricular assist device operating conditions. The CFD hemolysis model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is assessed at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across all 13 credibility factors; 7 factors were formally assessed and 6 remain flagged as epistemic gaps. This package conforms to the Minimal profile and provides sufficient evidence for a conditional acceptance determination. Intended use scope is described narratively above rather than in a structured ContextOfUse object.",
