    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team conditionally accepted this package under the Minimal profile on the basis that the CFD hemolysis model provides sufficient low-risk exploratory evidence for the stated clinical research application. Six factors remain as documented epistemic gaps requiring resolution before any regulatory submission. The Minimal profile acceptance reflects the exploratory rather than regulatory nature of the current use.",
